******
[2] Cholera - Nigeria (Rivers State)
Date: Wed 14 Jan 2015
Source: Pulse [edited]
http://pulse.ng/health/in-rivers-20-die-in-fresh-cholera-outbreak-id3408391.html


Health officials say 20 people have died of cholera in the Adoni Local Government Area of Rivers State. This was disclosed by the State Commissioner for Health, Sampson Parker on Wed 14 Jan 2015. Parker also said, via a statement, that about 171 cases of the disease had been recorded since the beginning of an outbreak on 5 Jan 2015.

The commissioner however assured members of the public that the state government would tackle the scourge head on saying that 2 treatment centers had been established in 2 of the worst hit communities.

[Byline: 'Jola Sotubo]

