******
[4] Cholera - India (Gujarat)
Date: Thu 15 Jan 2015
Source: Desh Gujarat [edited]
http://deshgujarat.com/2015/01/15/news-in-brief-from-across-gujarat-114/


District administration of Narmada has declared all villages in a 10 km [6 mi] radius of Rajpipla town [Narmada district, Gujarat] as cholera affected. There are nearly 50 villages covered in this area.

